00:09:59,260 --> 00:10:01,230
Did it begin with my bad mouth?

269
00:10:01,230 --> 00:10:03,000
This really good story?

270
00:10:05,530 --> 00:10:12,200
Was it when I said the clothes

271
00:10:05,530 --> 00:10:12,200
you were wearing didn't fit you?

