00:23:13,560 --> 00:23:14,890
"Number 2"      - What are you--

506
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:21,130
Well, it was a 1 digit code, so I could easily call him

507
00:23:21,130 --> 00:23:23,200
And quickly      - I got it

508
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:26,070
Calling you was quick cause you were registered early

509
00:23:26,070 --> 00:23:30,380
You said "You're Kimu, so you're going NImu"

